         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/1/81 ¶ Let me offer my best felicitation to the new year, dear Dr Beccari. May it be to you one of happiness &amp; health! Should you see Madame Smillie, the poor Lady, who lost her last most accomplish...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.01.01c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Odoardo Beccari</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">University of Florence, Science Library: Botany, Archives, Beccari 12/32.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/1/81</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Let me offer my best felicitation to the new year, dear Dr Beccari. May it be to you one of happiness &amp; health! Should you see Madame Smillie, the poor Lady, who lost her last most accomplished child in your city,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to O. Beccari, 23 September 1880 (in this edition as 80-09-23a).</p>
               </note> then pray give her also my best wishes for the new year.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have just purchased the two volumes of Signor D'Albertis on his Papuan travels, in which you give a list of his plants.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Albertis (1880). Beccari provided two appendices: 'Notes on the plants collected by Sig. L. M. D'Albertis in New Guinea', vol. 2, pp. 391–5, and 'Catalogue of the plants of the Fly River, 1877', vol. 2, pp. 396–400.</p>
               </note> I have received the specimens of <name key="Mimosa%20saligna">Mimosa saligna</name> of Labill.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to O. Beccari, 1 September 1880 (in this edition as 80-09-01a).</p>
               </note> They represent two species, one probably from West Australia, if not both. I will try to make them out, when the jurors work for the intercolonial Exhibition is over.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1880-1.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wishing you every success in your great labors on the Sunda- &amp; Papua-Flora, I remain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I shall only be able to make a return-sending of dried plants, when the Exhibition work is over.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I enjoy the friendship of the Marquis &amp; Marchioness of Toverena here very much</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Best salutations to Signor D'Albertis.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Mimosa%20saligna">Mimosa saligna</name>
            </p>
